    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically flawless E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, providing linear power delivery and telepathic handling. The chassis remains rigid, supported by a refreshed suspension setup that retains original geometry. With zero oil leaks, a perfectly mapped ECU, and impeccable paint clarity, this is a collector-grade vehicle for the purist.",
