      "description": "Presenting an absolute time capsule: this vehicle is in pristine, showroom-floor condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating that highlights the flawless bodywork\u2014free of even the slightest swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the hand-stitched leather remains supple and matte, lacking any bolster wear or creasing, and it still retains that distinctive new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and digital interface functions with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships and stored in a climate-controlled garage under a soft cover. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved specimen for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive service dossier.",
